question: Fight Night: Who will win - Vera or Sandhagen? (2023-03-25)
description:
This is a market group about UFC Fight Night, an upcoming mixed martial arts event produced by the Ultimate Fighting Championship that is scheduled to take place on March 25, 2023, at AT&T Center in San Antonio, Texas, USA.

This is a market on whether Marlon Vera or Cory Sandhagen will win their bout.

If Marlon Vera is declared the winner of this bout, this market will resolve to “Vera”. If Cory Sandhagen is declared the winner of this bout, this market will resolve to “Sandhagen”.

If this fight is declared a draw, or if for any reason the match is not scored, postponed after April 1, 2023, 11:59:59 PM ET, or cancelled, this market will resolve 50-50.

question: Fight Night: Will Sandhagen win by finish? (2023-03-25)
description:
This is a market group about UFC Fight Night, an upcoming mixed martial arts event produced by the Ultimate Fighting Championship that is scheduled to take place on March 25, 2023, at AT&T Center in San Antonio, Texas, USA.

This is a market on whether Cory Sandhagen will win his upcoming bout with Marlon Vera by finish. To "win by finish" means winning by KO/TKO/disqualification, submission, or any other form of stoppage. Any decision made by the judges will not count as a finish.

This market will resolve to “Yes” if Cory Sandhagen wins his bout with Marlon Vera by finish. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

If for any reason the match is not scored, postponed after April 1, 2023 11:59:59 PM ET, or cancelled, this market will resolve 50-50.
